reviews.review_text: Went for dinner today and this restaurant exceeded my expectations! The service was great, with attentive staff who were knowledgeable and helpful with providing recommendations. The food was amazing!  The chicken were juicy and flavorful! However, they are still a bit spicy for me even though I ordered plain.  We loved the halloumi cheese and that yummy egg dessert too!!! Plus the cozy ambiance added an extra touch of comfort to the dining experience. Highly recommended!

The food I had was very great, I havent taken so much picture of it because I was too excited to dig in, it definitely looks delicious and boy I was not wrong   I also admire the place while waiting for my food, the ambiance was great and I really appreciate a warm and cozy environment especially whenever I eat. Also, the staff are super welcoming and nice. I will definitely go back! If you havent but already checking this out, you should come too. You will not regret any single bit of your visit. Definitely will recommend this to my friends and relatives.

I just got home and the first thing I did was give this restaurant a 5 star review. The food was outstanding. The place is nice. The staff were nice and respectful as well. Will definitely visit and eat here again.

I had food on friday and didnt expect the place to be busy. The food is great I had double skewers and spicy kale caesar salad. The portion size was generous and the staff are kind and very helpful, ensuring that I left the restaurant fully satisfied.

Peri Peri is a hidden gem for food enthusiasts, and their Peri Mac is an absolute knockout! The creamy mac n cheese with a peri peri kick is a flavor explosion that you wont want to miss. The ambiance is inviting, and the staff is friendly. My taste buds are still celebrating this unforgettable dining experience!

I recently tried Nandos chicken and rice bowl, and I must say, it exceeded my expectations in both taste and service. The chicken was perfectly grilled and seasoned with Nandos signature flavors, offering a delicious and slightly spicy kick. The rice was fluffy and well-cooked, complementing the chicken beautifully. What truly stood out, though, was the excellent customer service. The staff was welcoming, attentive, and ready to assist with any requests. They made my dining experience even more enjoyable. Overall, Nandos chicken and rice bowl not only satisfied my taste buds but also left me impressed with their top-notch customer service. Ill definitely be returning for more.

Definitely put this restaurant on your list when you re in Canada. I went to this restaurant simply because I am craving for some chicken but surprisingly their food is superb! The chicken flavor is authentic and the variety of their sauces are exquisite, surely a good pair with their grilled chicken. The chicken is moist and the rice is cooked into perfection. The service are over the top, the staff are very hospitable which I enjoyed. Love the overall experience and will definitely come back here again.

THIS   IS   THE   BEST   CHICKEN   WRAP   I HAVE EVER EATEN   THE JUICY AND FLAVOURFUL CHICKEN DIDNT MAKE THE VEGGIES SOGGY. IT HAS THE RIGHT CRUNCH AND THE WRAP DOESNT OVERWHELM THE FILLING. EVERYTHING IS PERFECT. WORTH THE TRY AND WILL DEFINITELY TRY AGAIN AND AGAIN AND AGAIN! THE STAFF IS VERY COURTEOUS TOO. I LOVE EVERYTHING ABOUT THIS RESTAURANT. EXCEEDED MY EXPECTATIONS. KUDOS!

I ate here yesterday and the chicken are tender and juicy. Its my first time trying Nandos and I like the lemon and herb flavor. I recommend the halloumi stick as well. The place is warm and I like it since weather is a bit cold. The staff are accommodating and very nice. Definitely will comeback with my family and friends here!

One of the best chicken we had. It was cook perfectly for us. Its juicy and flavorful. All Staff are accommodating and nice. I ask the female staff what she could recommend and she is vey helpful. So i ended up ordering plain chicken and the mango lime wings. And the peri mac is good and my kid likes it. I think my all time fave now is this Nandos!
Great service, fresh food, good portions. Very friendly staff. Vegetarian options: Amazing flame grilled Brussels sprouts
Eat here tonight and I love the service, ambiance and the food is really authentic. I love how tender and juicy the chicken is. Will definitely go back and bring my family and friends next time.

I went yesterday to Nandos and I was greeted in a really warm way and given a nice booth seat, the staff was very friendly and took their time to give me recommendations on what to eat and the service was fairly quick. The taste of the food was good, nicely cooked, juicy and tasty. I would recommend this location a lot.

The chicken is just so tender and mouthwatering. I visit here with my girlfriend usually every week now they even know me by face and show me really well. my girlfriend is happy after eating her food and that keeps me relaxed lol. both the manager and supervisor were nice to us.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Surjeet, that s what we love to hear! We can t wait to see you again soon!

reviews.review_text: I recently dined at Nando s Kerrisdale and ordered their Peri Ranch Crunch Salad, and it was an absolute delight! The combination of fresh greens, crispy chicken, and the unique peri ranch dressing made this salad a true winner. The flavors were perfectly balanced, and the portion size was just right. The ambiance at Nando s Kerrisdale was also pleasant, providing a comfortable and welcoming dining experience. I ll definitely be returning to try more of their delicious offerings. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a tasty and healthy meal option!
My friends and I ate dinner here everything was delicious. Ordered Plain ish but still spicy for my palate but will definitely come back.
Good place to eat. Happy mood

Great Nandos outlet with ample seating for large groups. The food quality is as per expectations from any Nandos The chicken sandwich is great as well as the grilled chicken. Price is slightly on the higher end as other outlets. Service is a little slow but the food is brought to the table. Nandos has more drink options than any other restaurant chain!

I have tried different nandos branch but this one is the best! There chicken is so tender and juicy. Also, the crew was very accommodating and friendly.

I ordered the halloumi sticks, halloumi salad, chicken wings, and hummus with peri-peri drizzle. My friend and I enjoyed everything and the staff were very friendly. Missed eating at Nandos Kerrisdale.

reviews.review_text: We tried Nandos for the first time and it was such a blast!! We loved it. Everything was super tasty: the chicken was well cooked with an amazing chargrill flavour (until we tasted yours, we had given up the idea of being able to eat a good rotisserie chicken in Vancouver), the garlic mashed potatoes was really well seasoned, the garlic bread was good though the portion was a bit small, the fries were good quality and the best of the meal was definitely the natas... So perfect! Im a former pastry chef and can tell you these little treats are paradise - theres a crispy crust, the whole thing is then melting in your mouth and you can only become addicted to this amazing taste!! Thanks Nandos for having offered us such a wonderful lunch today, youre definitely our new fav chicken spot of Van!!

Nandos has been my go-to for many years and I have continuously recommended it to family and friends. Best place on the market.

I love the chicken here! Its so delicious! Ive only tried the 1/4 chicken and Peri Peri fries, but its just so good that I havent been able to bring myself to try something else! When you arrive, the hostess will give you a table. Then you order and pay for your food from the front counter and gather your cutlery and condiments from a side area before returning to your table. Once your food is prepared, a server will bring out your food to your table and will occasionally check on you to see if you need anything else. Its a bit of a different system, but it works.

reviews.review_text: My experience was so pleasant; I thought I would definitely write a good review for Nandos. The interior is really nice and comfortable, lovely music. I am impressed at how the three different Nandos I have been in, in Ireland, England and here in Vancouver, have all been such high quality from the interior and music, staff and delightedly the food! Despite the food taking longer than expected, the staff simply came down and told me it would take a bit longer, which was totally fine. I appreciated them coming down, and thats all they had to prevent small little thing like delayed food turning into a disaster experience. The food was delicious once it arrived! Well worth the wait. I ordered the half chicken and peri fries. I think they even gave me extra chicken because of the wait. Some of the nicest I have ever tasted! Freshly cooked and succulent. Great Staff Great atmosphere Delicious food Im looking forward to my next visit. Nandos has definitely acquired me as a fan! :) Thank you!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Thank you for taking the time to get in touch and let us know you re all fired up Andrew! Looking forward to having you share your next Nando s experience with us soon!
